{% block response_format %}
RESPONSE FORMAT
You must respond with a single JSON object, no prose outside the JSON, matching this schema:
{
  "thinking": "free-form chain of thought for this turn (not persisted, not re-shown)",
  "strategic_plan_update": null | "new plan text" (null = keep prior; string replaces prior),
  "tactical_plan": "your immediate next steps (replaces prior)",
  "subgoals_update": { "add": ["new subgoal text", ...], "mark_done": [index, ...] },
  "lessons_to_add": ["things you learned this turn"],
  "action": "ACTION_NAME"  // must be one of the actions listed above
}

Rules:
- `action` is required; everything else has sensible defaults.
- `thinking` is discarded immediately after this turn. Use it for scratch reasoning.
- Your strategic_plan, tactical_plan, subgoals, and lessons persist to the next turn.
- You may rewrite your plans or subgoals freely; you cannot retract lessons.
{% endblock %}
